height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/9YICpjeGsbE?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>今年晚些时候，乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/disturbed-announce-the-sickness-25th-anniversary-tour-uk-europe-with-megadeth-buy-tickets-3840693">将在英国和欧洲进行17场演出</a>，这是上述标志性首张专辑《 Turn 25》的庆祝活动的一部分。</p><p>其中包括在伯明翰，都柏林，曼彻斯特，伦敦和格拉斯哥举行的演出，并看到来自Thrash Metal Pioneers <a href="/artists/megadeth">Megadeth</a>的支持。请访问<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/disturbed-tickets/artist/710396?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=w5HRQ%3A3B9xyPUUd0HkSfkSRTUks3yKyE2VNEVg0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>获取任何剩余门票。</p><p>今年夏天晚些时候，德拉曼（Draiman）还将前往英国<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/black-sabbath-final-show-birmingham-july-2025-metalla-slayer-pantera-line-up-tickets-3835042">参加Black Sabbath的最后现场表演</a>，该表演将在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/metallica">Metallica</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/slayer">Slayer</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pantera">Pantera</a>等的支持下在伯明翰举行。</p><p>该帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/disturbed-have-a-lot-of-stuff-recorded-for-next-album-reveals-dan-donegan-3847781">扰乱了下一张专辑的“有很多录制的东西”，Demaled Dan Donegan</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
